data.label: Mozilla NSS
data.description: 网络安全服务 (NSS) 是一组库，旨在支持跨平台开发支持安全的客户端和服务器应用程序。使用 NSS 构建的应用程序可以支持 SSL v3、TLS、PKCS #5、PKCS #7、PKCS #11、PKCS #12、S/MIME、X.509 v3 证书和其他安全标准。

data.label: Mozilla NSS
data.description: Network Security Services (NSS) is a set of libraries designed to support cross-platform development of security-enabled client and server applications. Applications built with NSS can support SSL v3, TLS, PKCS #5, PKCS #7, PKCS #11, PKCS #12, S/MIME, X.509 v3 certificates, and other security standards.
